<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Shubha Vivah</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e91e63 0%, #9c27b0 100%);
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #333333;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .content p {
        color: #666666;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e91e63 0%, #9c27b0 100%);
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #999999;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Shubha Vivah</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome, <%= firstName %>!</h2>
        <p>
          Thank you for joining Shubha Vivah. We're excited to help you find your perfect life
          partner.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your account has been successfully created. You can now log in and complete your profile
          to start your journey.
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: center">
          <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Complete Your Profile</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Shubha Vivah Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Shubha Vivah. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you did not sign up, please ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
